===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

#A male given name, sometimes a short form of [[Leonard]]; compare [[Leon]].
#{{constellation}}: One of the twelve [[constellation]]s of the [[zodiac]], shaped approximately like a [[lion]] and containing the bright star [[Regulus]].
#{{astrology}}: The zodiac sign for the [[Lion]], covering July 23&ndash;August 22.

